\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ the one who commits evil and the good to the one who does good. [Lam. Rabbah].) Therefore, what 
\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ should a man complain about, if not about his sins?  
